Reprove 3.47a
by contradiciton

  ¬(¬(p ⋀ q) ≡ ¬p ⋁ ¬q)
=    〈 Distributivity of ¬ over ≡ 〉
  ¬¬(p ⋀ q) ≡ ¬p ⋁ ¬q
=    〈 Double negation 〉
  p ⋀ q ≡ ¬p ⋁ ¬q
=    〈 Golden rule 〉
  p ≡ q ≡ p ⋁ q ≡ ¬p ⋁ ¬q
=    〈 (3.32) 〉
  q ≡ p ⋁ ¬q ≡ ¬p ⋁ ¬q
=    〈 Distributivity of ⋁ over ≡ 〉
  q ≡ (p ≡ ¬p) ⋁ ¬q
=    〈 (3.15) 〉
  q ≡ false ⋁ ¬q
=    〈 Identity of ⋁ 〉
  q ≡ ¬q
=    〈 (3.15) 〉
  false  ╱╱

